-- Mark Webber Wins Hungarian Formula 1 Grand Prix, Leads Drivers' Standings
-- Peter-Joseph Hegarty
-- 2010-08-01T13:46:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-01/mark-webber-wins-hungarian-formula-1-grand-prix-leads-drivers-standings.html

          
          
             Mark Webber of Red Bull won today’s
Hungarian Grand Prix and takes the lead in the Formula One
drivers’ standings. Ferrari’s Fernando Alonso was second and Red
Bull’s Sebastian Vettel third.  
          
          


  


        